into a single Postgres identifier, which\nPostgres rejects at parse time when it doesn't exist — preventing the\ninner SQL from being evaluated. This is exactly the defense already\nin place for the parallel sink in getCriteriaSqlClause.\n\nNote: the master/2.40-2.42 backports use SqlUtils.quote() and ship\ncompanion regression tests in SqlViewControllerIntegrationTest. On\n2.37 the matching defense API is statementBuilder.columnQuote() and\nthe regression test class does not exist, so only the fix is applied.\n\nAI Assisted\n\nRefs GHSA-pwmg-mvjw-4m23, DHIS2-21425","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"4ec7cf8ec3f7d89a0c660c48ebcec72cec870f91","tree_id":"726c74e846898295cef31329c33bef671468c09e","timestamp":"2026-06-09T10:25:24Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. Conta